<h3>Where to Start</h3>
<p><strong>If your clients are millennials or Gen Z:</strong> Instagram and TikTok. These demographics scroll these platforms daily. Short-form video drives the highest organic reach in 2026.</p>
<p><strong>If your clients are professionals or corporate EAP referrals:</strong> LinkedIn. Workplace wellness content performs well and positions you as a specialist.</p>
