<h2>Chapter 2: Content That Builds Trust</h2>
<p>The biggest mistake therapists make on social media is trying to provide therapy through their posts. Your content should educate, normalize, and build trust. It should not diagnose, treat, or replace a session.</p>
<h3>The 60/20/15/5 Content Mix</h3>
