<td>60%</td>
<td>Myth-busting, coping strategies, research insights, therapy process explainers</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Engagement</td>
<td>20%</td>
<td>Polls, quizzes, "this or that" posts, Q&amp;A boxes, comment prompts</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Behind-the-scenes</td>
<td>15%</td>
<td>Office setup, favorite tools, day-in-the-life, book recommendations</td>
</tr>
<tr>
