<h3>When Social Media Makes Sense</h3>
<p>Social media is worth the investment when:</p>
<ul>
<li>Your ideal clients are millennials or Gen Z (they check social before booking)</li>
<li>You enjoy creating content (forced content reads as forced)</li>
<li>You have 3 to 5 hours per week to dedicate consistently</li>
<li>You want to build a personal brand beyond your local area</li>
</ul>
